originalText.text:
I was quite concern with my hearing and I decided to call the Wednesday before Thanksgiving. The office was closed so  I left a message. Well  I got a call on Saturday at eight am to let me know that  I could see the doctor that same day at 11 am. That day of my appointment I met two wonderful people.
The doctor's assistant is efficient, courteous and kind. And the Doctor is just amazing.  He is knowledgeable in his field, and he really cares about the human being that is before him. He thoroughly explained the problem and the procedure that I needed to undergo. He is funny, kind and also a great conversionist.  Thank you for the great service.
